title: What's this font? Seen it everywhere!
content:
I have seen this typeface everywhere, but I don’t know what it is. Help, please?

| Attachment | Size |
| --- | --- |
| [Stella\_3Dskew\_72dpi copy.jpg](http://web.archive.org/web/20090924020720/http:/typophile.com/files/Stella_3Dskew_72dpi%20copy.jpg) | 131.9 KB |
author: parolex

comments.content: It’s not [Cyclone from H&FJ](http://web.archive.org/web/20090924020720/http:/typography.com/fonts/font_overview.php?productLineID=100003), but they are quite similar if you can’t track down what you’re looking for.
